    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Children are the Lord’s heritage, so dear in God’s eyes!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just like arrows in quiver aimed for Satan’s demise!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Even though they might trouble us and vex our soul,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We must learn to recover them and not let them go!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What a wonderful church life we are living today!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With the saints of all ages, Christ in us we’ll display!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Eating, playing, exhorting—we’re God’s family;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Everyone has a function to build up corporately!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, we thank You for all the ones You’ve placed here with us"
